Knee deep is a reference to the depth of something. As the name would suggest, whatever the thing or things are, they generally amount to the depth equivalent with the height of one's knees while standing. The reference is very general, and obviously varies from person to person, which can sometimes lead to confusion, though not that often enough to the point where it normally becomes a chronic problem.
